{"tid":200052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【打和】【一部撼26部】曾志偉認失言：我覺得係需要道歉","createTime":"2017-04-13T15:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T04:21:29.000Z","uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e663c134bdcb1b18a97e5a3d544e71790a8d678e","tid":200052,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"講到姜皓文（黑仔）事件，志偉自言當下第一時間都想道歉，「我上台只係想講『一部賠26部』，我係想鼓勵黑仔，話俾佢知後面嘅機會就係佢喇，但係都唔知點解自己講咗一部贏（編按：應是「撼」）26部，我完全冇呢個用意。若然令大家有所誤會，我覺得係需要道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170413/56561551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170413%2F56561551&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=50112487\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170413%2F56561551&h=c96ee3f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170413/56561551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75208ad9a482b2fbb7ed39d1a4fb8d07d0109b62","tid":200052,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:21:29.000Z","msg":"通常成材都係靠俾人串一獲先上到位"}]}